race.description: Hahn Super Dry Country Boosted Hcp (C1)
race.comment: CONCOCTION (2) broke through in style at Gunnedah, putting them away with authority. Lightly raced and clearly on the up, he looks well placed to back it up and go right on with it. GIRLY POP (8) returns and is a noted fresh performer, narrowly missing here over the track and trip when resuming last campaign. Draws well and can make a bright return. CITY GOLD SPEED (3) has been thereabouts of late, fighting hard in his past two runs. Honest type who deserves a win. RHODESIAN DIAMOND (4) was edged out in a tight finish last start and brings solid form to this. Can figure again with any luck in running.
